column5: Certainly don't disagree with those statements. Big oil can eat it. I hope I'm wrong but I bet gas is $5 a gallon in a few yrs in this aftermath. The chickens will come home to roost for the US basically giving money away at ridiculous levels. Ridiculous prices of goods and services isn't too far away
